flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[User logs in]
    B --> C[Scan or select bin]
    C --> D[Validate bin and part details]
    D --> E[Update bin status]
    E --> F[Generate report]
    F --> G{Data valid?}
    G -- Yes --> H[Save / Submit]
    G -- No --> I[Show error and correct data]
    I --> B
    H --> J([End])